flowRoot.flowPara: free educational materials for free speakers

I want to build a collection of speaking exercises that speaking clubs around the world can use for free. The educational material will consist of speeches, speech evaluations and meeting facilitation exercises. For this idea to work, I need your help.
To be useful for any speaking organization free of charge, the Creative Commons BY-NC-SA License will be used.
